author: senh
title: Murphy HRs again; Mets beat Arrieta, Cubs for 2-0 NLCS lead
text: BING NEWS: Murphy HRs again; Mets beat Arrieta, Cubs for 2-0 NLCS lead NEW YORK (AP) — Daniel Murphy homered off yet another ace. Noah Syndergaard turned in one more outstanding outing from the Mets' collection of studly young starters. Power, pitching, plus some dazzling defense are falling into place for New York.
